This has been something we have been seeing more and more reports of recently actually.  We investigated internally, and it looks like there was a problem on the back-end several days ago causing matches to either be severely delayed in loading or just straight missing.  We have resolved the issue and now the system is hard at work back-filling these matches and displaying them properly.  It may take a couple of days yet before it is all back to normal however!
